definition.value: A member of the class of  chalcones that is trans-chalcone substituted by methoxy groups at positions 2', 4 and 4' and hydroxy groups at positions 3' and 6'.
A member of the class of chalcones that is trans-chalcone substituted by a hydroxy group at position 2' and methoxy groups at positions 2, 3, 4, 6, 3', 4', 5' and 6'.
The hydrochloride salt of paroxetine. It is an antidepressant drug.
